{"data":{"page":{"id":"e9f2a398-8c86-570c-90fc-1435b521bb30","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/lovul/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website</a>\n</p>\n<p>L’Òvul was a cultural magazine I got involved with. It was made with love by friends in Barcelona. I built this microsite to display the latest issues of the magazine, info and dates of upcoming events and a few artworks.</p>\n<p>Most of the content is now offline, but you can have a look at the quirky animations ;-)</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/56dd4abb54a948cde4db4eafa7a58f35/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/56dd4abb54a948cde4db4eafa7a58f35/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/56dd4abb54a948cde4db4eafa7a58f35/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/56dd4abb54a948cde4db4eafa7a58f35/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/56dd4abb54a948cde4db4eafa7a58f35/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>","fields":{"prefix":"2002-12-16"},"frontmatter":{"title":"L'ovul","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lovul/","source":"work"}}